<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2020-06-30</DATELINE><TITLE>Type 1 interferons as a potential treatment against COVID-19</TITLE><BODY>Abstract Type 1 interferons have a broad antiviral activity in vitro and are currently evaluated in a clinical trial to treat MERS-CoV. In this review, we discuss preliminary data concerning the potential activity of type 1 interferons on SARS-CoV-2, and the relevance of evaluating these molecules in clinical trials for the treatment of COVID-19.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>